{"tid":1080201,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"Beyond 最後一首歌進化論，林夕神級填詞","createTime":"2019-03-27T12:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T14:06:38.000Z","uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"15b13d238a0f2d3b5fe078ad983bf76c0a0e671d","tid":1080201,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:25:39.000Z","msg":"一首歌詞講哲理，神到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aaqhnmZziJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaaqhnmZziJg&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTlwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=f945c8ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aaqhnmZziJg</a><br />\nBeyond <br />\n<br />\n進化論(Evolution)<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕<br />\n作曲：黃貫中<br />\n<br />\n玩具代代進化　不見得叫憎惡變相愛<br />\n天已老　地未老　進步<br />\n菩提代代進化　不見得叫爭鬥變寬恕<br />\n天已老　地未老　進步<br />\n紅塵代代進代　不見得叫鮮血變花瓣<br />\n天已老　地未老　進步<br />\n一天一天　昇天<br />\n一生一生　超生<br />\n<br />\n* 上帝未肯對化石天天修補<br />\n上帝未必答應明天更加好<br />\n茁壯的不會更茁壯<br />\n但你我每秒鐘會更蒼老 *<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慾望日夜進化　不免需索需索再需索<br />\n天已老　地未老　進步<br />\n大地日夜進化　一切飢渴飢渴更飢渴<br />\n天已老　地未老　進步<br />\n一天一天　昇天<br />\n一生一生　超生<br />\n<br />\nRepeat *<br />\n<br />\n循環或是進化　總要吸氣呼氣再吸氣<br />\n天已老　地未老　進步<br />\n萬物日夜進化　將最可怕改到更可怕<br />\n天已老　地未老　進步"},{"pid":"50418ccbffa1be0c494e2e2843eb75f71043aacb","tid":1080201,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:28:16.000Z","msg":"十八都好神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XtLms2nqMEs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXtLms2nqMEs&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTlwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=23b3c2c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XtLms2nqMEs</a><br />\n<br />\nBeyond <br />\n<br />\n十八<br />\n<br />\n作詞：黃貫中<br />\n作曲：黃貫中<br />\n<br />\n從不知天高與地厚　漸學會很多困憂<br />\n也試過制度和自由<br />\n也許不再沒有　又或者不想再追究<br />\n我發覺這地球原來很大　但靈魂已經敗壞<br />\n<br />\n* 如用這歌　可以代表我<br />\n幫我為你加一點付和<br />\n假使可以　全沒隔阻<br />\n可以代表我　可以伴你不管福或禍<br />\n這樣已是很足夠 *<br />\n<br />\n從相簿中跟我又再會面　輕翻起每一片<br />\n十八歲再度浮面前<br />\n也許一切在變　又或者始終沒打算<br />\n我與我分開已很遠很遠　在浪潮兜兜轉轉<br />\nRepeat * *<br />\n這樣已是很足夠"},{"pid":"5da3feeebffc3517f2284b7884471415822a6584","tid":1080201,"uid":12498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"左右手屌打啦"},{"pid":"6038ad6af92021ac27f5dd4a18f751d99fddd58a","tid":1080201,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5da3feeebffc3517f2284b7884471415822a6584","tid":1080201,"uid":12498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"左右手屌打啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"基佬歌"}]}